WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:06.280
- I have started getting more
and more into Gems lately.

2
00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.510
It's sort of like my own little team.

3
00:00:09.510 --> 00:00:13.200
So I have one Gem that serves
as my like project manager,

4
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:15.960
and this then helps me create other Gems.

5
00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:17.160
I call it my Gem-erator.

6
00:00:18.060 --> 00:00:20.910
So, this Gem is specifically meant to,

7
00:00:20.910 --> 00:00:22.380
one, do project management.

8
00:00:22.380 --> 00:00:26.130
But when I need a specific
thing, like writing ad copy,

9
00:00:26.130 --> 00:00:29.103
it then will help me create
a Gem for writing ad copy.

10
00:00:30.060 --> 00:00:31.710
So I have very niche use cases

11
00:00:31.710 --> 00:00:34.530
when I want it to have
specific sort documentation

12
00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:36.510
or a specific tone of voice.

13
00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:38.647
And so then it helps me sort of dictate,

14
00:00:38.647 --> 00:00:41.490
"Okay, this is a task
for your ad copy Gem.

15
00:00:41.490 --> 00:00:44.430
This is a task for your
like messaging Gem."

16
00:00:44.430 --> 00:00:45.970
And that is my like go-to.